social_posts.post_text: Bounce to the beat in @jardin_lasvegas 💚 #jardinlasvegas

Hiiii world! I’ve been in my own cocoon these past couple months focused on health & healing. Shedding old versions of myself making room for 2023 vibrant meeeee. For now.. I miss you!!! Sending love and light 💡 Crykit

Can’t believe this set was taken almost 10 years ago! I’ve lovvvved being photographed by @deeddebruno since the moment I stepped in front of her camera! She has an adorable energy paired with so much talent and creativity. I feel my most free and fierce authentic self with her :) LOVE YOU DEED! Also… my babe MUA  @thecelinarodriguez right before she moved from Vegas to LA to blow the F up! 😎✨😎

I’m still on ☁️9 & inspired by watching @atrak play last night.. I even woke up and started playing with effects manipulating sounds for fun! - 😆 loved every moment of opening up for this legend w/ my funky talented crew @thediscodivers !! Thank you @clubsodavegas & @weallscreamdtlv 🥳🥳🥳

📸 @djpdot
Wooo! Love this little #90s @savers_thrift haul today :)) there’s no more dressing rooms so you’re getting the at home try on with me for the first time 😄

Wooo! Our Neon Dreams came true playing at @area15official Massive ✨
Soooo much fun playing B2B w/ @soldevomusic I felt like I was on a trampoline bouncing from the contagious good energy and bass 😆😆
Thank you @noahcastrophoto for capturing our energy & lasting memories of an amazing night :))

MUA: @cyoungmakeup
HAIR: @amberharlan
DYED SUIT: @tripleaquarian
CANDY BRA: @vidakush
SOCKS: @jardin_lasvegas (💚always)

This was such a cool experience 🥰🤩 thank you @area15official for having me play at the Secret Garden x @meow__wolf activation ✨💕 loved playing trippy beats immersed in visual art!! the @sts9 community / show was such a vibe! @cyoungmakeup with the perfect rave fairy look :)

Last night was caaauuuute! There was a sparkle in the air playing with @jazlynrich at @lamonarosalv 💕 luckily @andys1hrphoto captured this magic moment 🙏🏼😁

Pink attire suggested.. @jardin_lasvegas came in clutch w/ this pink pretty girls hat 💕 #jardinlasvegas

I’m in my happy place playing happy music tonight @weallscreamdtlv 🥰

Vocal / Disco / Tech house on the rooftop :)) wooooo!

📸 @romes.raw 
* amazing vintage TROOP jacket thanks to @_bowiereyes_

I can’t believe it’s been a decade since moving to Las Vegas to become a full time DJ! It’s a dream come true that I never knew I had 😆 the intentional music I choose and the energy I bring while playing is the secret sauce. Music has the power to move people, it’s not forced it’s felt. I’m so grateful to be a creator of FUN and conductor of memorable experiences:))
Please enjoy this 2013 video by @daltoncampbell .. I did :)

Took my Mom to @prettydone gallery shop opening 😄😄 so much fun art on all types of mediums! I loved seeing the diversity of Pretty Done art collectors.. from kids to grandparents to fitness, music, and sneaker heads… his art brings joy. Congrats Adam! 🍻 (mugs filled with cold brew lol)
* I had to wear the only one in existence basketball jersey set & custom 5 panel hat :)) the double camo design shorts turned into socks.. which BTW I bought every pair of camo design socks .. 9 designs 😆

Oooo… Now available for your listening pleasure.. my set from @skratchbastid @bastidsbbq Las Vegas!

Being a part of this night was so special in so many ways! To have a platform to play funk, soul, hip hop, & most of all remixes and edits reimagined by some of my favorite producers was a blessing … and to play while legends & OGs are listening?! I couldn’t stop dancing in the cyphers afterwards as every set was ridiculous. All while rocking a custom ice dyed BBQ edition set by @tripleaquarian … 🔥 🔥
Thank you @skratchbastid for bringing your amazing party to Vegas.. a night I’ll never forget!! 

Special s/o @jardin_lasvegas + @macagencylv + @weallscreamdtlv + @pioneerdjusa + @selvareyrum for making the best party of 2023 happen!

📸: @vehgus + @lotusvalentinevisuals + @technicolor_lv

☝🏻💚☝🏽💚☝🏾💚☝🏿

Skipping through the cactus gardens in custom ice dyed @jardin_lasvegas 💚🫶🏻

It’s so much fun to collaborate with @tripleaquarian & see her tie & dye artistry transform a neutral tee & hat into a showstopper 🤩 it’s now a conversational piece that sparks joy and connection 😊

#jardinlasvegas #icedye #cactusgarden

Woooo! It’s here… @lifeisbeautiful 2023 🤩 The best time of the year in #dtlv !!! I’m excited to be playing inside of @meow__wolf exhibit today 9:15-11:00pm & Sunday w/ @thediscodivers 6-7:30pm & 9-10:30pm ✨🥳✨ Immersive art & connection through feel good music :)) living the dream!

🪄 love it when my outfit matches the event decor ✨
The blazer is a 1 of 1 custom @prettydone design 🤩

This was such a FUN @prismdjs booking & incredible experience working with @dj_tessa 🫶🏻

MUA 💕 @spencerlopez2.0

The creative energy was flowing at the  @meow__wolf  x @lifeisbeautiful space!

I had an incredible experience playing inside this super cool FUNhouse! All hand built, painted, & designed by Las Vegas artists this space offered a place for exploration, conversation, dancing, playing bingo, and other surprises to spark the imagination. 

The perfect space to wear @tripleaquarian ice dyed magic! Alien spaceship shirt, bodysuit, pants, hat, and bandana all were ice dyed for that custom trip drip look 🤩

* ALL IMAGES: Kurt Lubas, Courtesy of Meow Wolf

#meowwolf #lifeisbeautiful #lifeisbeautifulfestival #aliens #spaceship #icedye #icedyed #femaledj #artfestival #lasvegasdj #ilovemylife #gratitude

Oooooo… Next week! I’m honored to be a part of @dynastyrockers 50th Anniversary in Las Vegas. I’ll be dancing the night away in my freshest fit with a perma smile amongst incredible dancers. Let’s goooo! Thank you @charliechillout for the invite 😎✨

Ooooo!!! I had the incredible opportunity to open for @marcrebillet and it was so much FUN!!! Excited to run it back tonight with theee loop daddy at @bbowlvegas :))

HAPPY 7 YEARS @jardin_lasvegas 💚🥳

I’m so grateful to be a part of this multi-award winning team that focuses on culture! Their parties have been top tier w/ legendary artists & DJs making an impactful mark on Las Vegas & around the globe. Not to mention their quality product sold by educated babe budtenders while dope DJs are playing live in store 💚😀💚

Big green hugs of nugs not drugs #jardinlasvegas

✨2024✨ PLAY and JOY as superpowers!

DJ CRYKIT is available for bookings to elevate your special event’s energy w/ high frequencies; especially in these times of global stress. A lighthouse of creativity playing music that invites humanity to unite in love and movement. Passionate about the art and challenge of curating crates that span across the globe, decades, & multi genres. I’m the perfect blend of cheese from Wisconsin, culture from San Francisco, and show business from Las Vegas :))

Watch and share the full 15 minute mix w/ anyone looking to book a professional, experienced, energetic, & FUN DJ 🤩
* open to GLOBAL travel, connections, opportunities, & gigs 🎶😃🎶 CHEERS
